title: Shooting of ‘Dishoom’ scenes swapped after John Abraham’s injury
text: Shooting of ‘Dishoom’ scenes swapped after John Abraham’s injury Monday, 19 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) The makers of action-adventure film 'Dishoom' have decided to swap actor John Abraham's action sequences with other scenes that require more dialogues.
